dct_description_sm: Published by Dehli Development Authority. Map is part of "Work studies relating to the preparation of the master plan for Delhi" Map Library does not have the companion text. Map includes legend. Map shows planning divisions, development zones; railroad lines, major highways, and rivers. Map is part of "Work studies relating to the preparation of the master plan for Delhi / prepared by Delhi Development Authority under the Delhi Development Act, 1957" Map Libarry does not have this companion text. Dehli Development Authority.
dct_publisher_sm: New Delhi : Commercial Offset Press Karol Bagh, New Delhi-5, [1956].
